  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And they were dishing it out in such a manner, in such a fast manner, that if you walked up and you didn't have your-- your canteen right there at the right spot, you miss the soup, and you would not get it anymore.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And so this was a kind of an extremely brutal concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And-- and the worst part was that we had no idea on where-- what is happening, what will be happening to us.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "It was only after a few days stay that, actually, a-- a SS guard came into our-- our barrack.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And the-- and the situation was so bad and crowded in this barrack that all we had for space for ourselves to exist in this barrack is to-- was to simply sit on the floor in one another's lap.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "That's how we stayed for hours and days, in one another's lap, because that's all the space that was [? allowed ?] for us in the barrack.",
      "word_count": 27
    }
  ],
